org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers.ASTNodeCompiler
public class APMFormulaCompilerNoPiecewise
extends org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers.FormulaCompiler

Produces an infix formula like FormulaCompiler but removes all the piecewise functions. They are replaced by an id that is unique if you are using the same FormulaCompilerNoPiecewise instance. The content of the piecewise function is put in a HashMap and is transformed to use if/then/else. This class is used for example to create an SBML2APM converter where (in APM) the piecewise operator is not supported.

Author:
Grigsby
